# Navigation + anchor integrity

When editing `navLinks` or section `id`s:

- Each `navLinks[].href` must match exactly one section `id` (e.g. `#probleme` → `id="probleme"`).
- No duplicate `id` values on the page.
- Renaming an anchor: update **both** `src/constants/index.js` and the section file.

## Home anchors (current)

| Nav label (approx.) | href | Section file | id |
|---------------------|------|--------------|-----|
